## Key Design Changes

| Area | Before | After |
|---|---|---|
| **Font** | Newsreader + Public Sans | Lora (display only) + Plus Jakarta Sans |
| **Hero heading** | 5-line serif stacked, unreadable | 2-line italic display, readable at a glance |
| **Trust cards** | 3-col overflow grid inside sidebar | Stacked icon cards, no overflow |
| **Login layout** | 2-col with redundant step cards | Centered single-column auth card |
| **Dashboard metrics** | Oversized cards with minimal info | Compact stat pills with icons |
| **Screening records** | 3-col card grid (noisy) | Clean HTML table with status badges |
| **Dashboard sidebar** | Filler "Screening Context" text | Removed; Add Child moved to nav |
| **Forgot password** | Two-col form with giant heading | Centered card matching login |
| **Terms** | Flat stacked sections | Sticky TOC + anchor-linked sections |
| **Buttons** | Gradient OK, weak hierarchy | Teal primary + ghost secondary, clear hierarchy |
| **Radius/shadows** | Over-rounded, excessive | Tighter, more product-like |

